Class HourlyEmployee

  • java.lang.Object
    • javaapplication4.Employee
      • javaapplication4.HourlyEmployee

  • public class HourlyEmployee
extends Employee
    Class Invariant: All objects have a name string, hire date, nonnegative wage rate, and nonnegative number of hours worked. A name string of "No name" indicates no real name specified yet. A hire date of Jan 1, 1000 indicates no real hire date specified yet.
